Package: mailmerge
Title: Mail Merge Using R Markdown Documents and 'gmailr'
Description: Mail merge using markdown documents and gmail. With this package
    you can parse markdown documents as the body of email, and the `yaml` header 
    to specify the subject line of the email.  Any '{}' braces in the email will be 
    encoded with 'glue::glue()'. You can preview the email in the RStudio viewer pane, and
    send (draft) email using 'gmailr'.
